definitions.definition: Ishmael , the first son of Abraham ; traditionally the ancestor of the Arabs .
A transliteration of the Macedonian male given name Исмаил ( Ismail ) .

main_definition: ( Islam ) Ishmael , the first son of Abraham ; traditionally the ancestor of the Arabs .
